"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"> ### 引言\\n>\\n> *本文为 Stablecoin DeFi策略系列第 4 篇，系列其它策略如下：*\\n>\\n> * *[$UST-$Mirror策略（Terra链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU)*\\n> * *[$UST-$MIM策略（ETH链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/Oz3Sdd4D5JZTZ3b13ABAaL2WjWi6_IQRDRjGH-jZtZI)*\\n> * *[$FTM-$TOMB策略（Fantom链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/rlWkMMbg2H9GlsuFVXAwyjfRu4gkcfYjNia7wAbbhRc)*\\n> * *[$ATOM-$OSMO策略（Cosmos链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/hAX73I66TcUTc5gCHbrjJ6vhor3Pi07fhtKMb9cw4Qo)*\\n> * *[$TIME Staking策略（Avalance链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/br12Nt9v13oMGoN1fv1PWt3oX5uAY89DUbqbf8PQJ88)*\\n> * *[稳定币 DeFi协议总结](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/vjhrsKgkRRA4B9cf7Sb5FpfKHziM7ckdzhqmBxLAvlg)*\\n>\\n> *其中涉及到的操作指南如下：*\\n>\\n> * *[$UST跨链指南（ETH链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/U5HcyR431ID0WwFItQa5k698jAzy3VBDtD-2ks-xYKM)*\\n\\n### 一、准备$LUNA 到 Keplr 钱包（Terra链）\\n\\n1. 在CEX（如Coinbase、Binance、Huobi等）上买入$BUSD/$USDT等稳定币，闪兑换成$LUNA（1 LUNA = 65.54 BUSD）；\\n2. 提现少量到Keplr钱包（Terra链），作为手续费；\\n\\n### 二、准备$LUNA 到 Keplr 钱包（Terra链）\\n\\n1. [Anchor](https://app.anchorprotocol.com/)或者[TerraStation](https://station.terra.money/)上提现 $UST，到 Keplr 钱包（Terra链）；\\n2. 在Keplr钱包（Terra链）确认$LUNA和$UST是否到账；\\n3. 如有需要，$UST 跨链策略如下：\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/U5HcyR431ID0WwFItQa5k698jAzy3VBDtD-2ks-xYKM](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/U5HcyR431ID0WwFItQa5k698jAzy3VBDtD-2ks-xYKM)\\n\\n### 三、IBC Transfer到ATOM链\\n\\n1. 进入[OSMOSIS](https://app.osmosis.zone/)，关联Keplr钱包；\\n2. 在「Assets」中找到Terra - UST，点击「Deposit」；\\n3. 在「Deposit IBC Asset」弹窗中，确认钱包跨链地址，输入准备存入Osmosis的$UST数量，点击Deposit，花费$LUNA作为手续费；\\n4. 在Keplr钱包（Osmosis链）确认$UST是否到账；\\n\\n### 四、组合ATOM-OSMO LP\\n\\n1. 点击左侧「Trade」，用一半$UST换$ATOM，一半$UST换$OSMO；\\n2. 点击左侧「Pools」，选择Pool #1（ATOM/OSMO），选择上方「Add Liquidity」，MAX所有OSMO（或者ATOM），组合ATOM / OSMO LP，剩余token可以单币质押；\\n3. 点击右侧「Start Earning」，选择14 days（APR 111.62%），MAX所有LP；\\n4. 确认交易；\\n\\n### 五、结束\\n\\n![WAGMI, Anon!](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/3rtGgJTEZMywy1huiH54z.jpeg?height=900&width=1600)\\n\\n## 策略汇总：\\n\\n## Terra(🌍,🌍)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU)\\n\\n## Ethereum(Ξ,Ξ)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/Oz3Sdd4D5JZTZ3b13ABAaL2WjWi6_IQRDRjGH-jZtZI](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/Oz3Sdd4D5JZTZ3b13ABAaL2WjWi6_IQRDRjGH-jZtZI)\\n\\n## Fantom(👻,👻)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/rlWkMMbg2H9GlsuFVXAwyjfRu4gkcfYjNia7wAbbhRc](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/rlWkMMbg2H9GlsuFVXAwyjfRu4gkcfYjNia7wAbbhRc)\\n\\n## Cosmos(⚛️,⚛️)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/hAX73I66TcUTc5gCHbrjJ6vhor3Pi07fhtKMb9cw4Qo](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/hAX73I66TcUTc5gCHbrjJ6vhor3Pi07fhtKMb9cw4Qo)\\n\\n## Avalance(🎩,🎩)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/br12Nt9v13oMGoN1fv1PWt3oX5uAY89DUbqbf8PQJ88](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/br12Nt9v13oMGoN1fv1PWt3oX5uAY89DUbqbf8PQJ88)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641203454,\"title\":\"$ATOM-$OSMO策略（⚛️，🪐）\"},\"digest\":\"ZejPfkkES_SrZyiDtiCMeZ_EZ2Aw8iqHVuQNoi5rXTU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2caAfafBc21f65697824f83aEAe6A9b1CB2a5B9D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SkVV_-Xl3k90FjwbifpvhCPhuiYzJWPRe2rXCGV2qRg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"AbCKotboCHNs6i9ApRJjBG7aQ6hUIVAR6yF-kgNSMH4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"vPzMVd23D3f32V0RzZro8MQRmW83yHpLrpWT_vedIdczT_EnZUv5KYAG5ShCx1U6-2rOiPPIdLfcZRXpchzuag\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xda5f1efe4c865be0f788eb7e7b166fd1f844e7f25aabb8713c46c2f05fe51695139aa85c3a7ae92e9481acb089405a35acb46181e57966fc9a492d23caad16551c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SkVV_-Xl3k90FjwbifpvhCPhuiYzJWPRe2rXCGV2qRg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"AbCKotboCHNs6i9ApRJjBG7aQ6hUIVAR6yF-kgNSMH4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"